Create the main layout of the TUI placeholders for each screen. 

Save the main layout to `../../packages/convo-lang-cli/src/lib/tui/main-layout.ts`

And save each screen to `../../packages/convo-lang-cli/src/lib/tui/{name}-layout.ts`

Export the main layout as function that accepts a single sprite and returns a screen that
wraps the passed sprite in the main layout:

``` ts
export const mainLayout=(sprite:SpriteDef):ScreenDef;
```

Then each screen should export a function that returns a sprite:

``` ts
export const settingsScreen=():ScreenDef=>{
    return mainLayout({
        // screen content here
    })
}
```

